<p><a id="TSJN-01-04-0560-kw-0001" class="keywordref" title="jump to Colo. Swearingen in text" href="#TSJN-01-04-0560-ks-0001">Colo. Swearingen</a>: Josiah? Swearingen (or Van Swearingen), county lieutenant of Berkeley from 1777 (Gwathmey, <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Hist. Reg. of Virginians in the Revolution</span>). See <a href="default.xqy?keys=TSJN-print-01-04-02-0793" class="document">TJs reply, 16 Feb. 1781</a>.</p></div>
